des:
YTE Home products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your robtic vacuum cleaner.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your robtic vacuum cleaner - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your YTE Home products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "YTE Home" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "YTE Home" app;
(3). You need to have some YTE Home devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "YTE Home" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "YTE Home" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "YTE Home" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "YTE Home", and you'll be navigated to "YTE Home" login page;
(9). Open "YTE Home" App, click More Service, choose "Alexa". Link with Verification Code, copy the Code, put code into the login page；
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on robtic vacuum cleaner.”
“Alexa, turn off robtic vacuum cleaner.”
